### Teste da API REST - E-commerce

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. Informações da API
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health/info
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 3. Listar Produtos
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 4. Buscar Produto por ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 5. Criar Novo Produto
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 999,
  "name": "Produto Teste",
  "price": 99.99
}

###

### 6. Adicionar Produto ao Carrinho
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/cart/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Teclado gamer",
  "price": 199.9
}

###

### 7. Buscar Produtos com Filtro
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search?field=nome&filter=teclado&exact=false
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 8. Registrar Usuário
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/register?user=teste&pwd=123456
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 9. Login de Usuário
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/login?user=teste&pwd=123456
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 10. Criar Endereço para Usuário
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/1/address
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rua": "Rua Teste",
  "numero": "123",
  "bairro": "Centro",
  "cidade": "São Paulo",
  "estado": "SP",
  "complement": "Apto 1",
  "cep": "01234-567"
}

###

### 11. Finalizar Pedido
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/finish
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "id": 1,
    "name": "Teclado gamer",
    "price": 199.9
  },
  {
    "id": 2,
    "name": "Mouse óptico",
    "price": 89.9
  }
]

###

### 12. Avaliar Pedido
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/evaluate?comment=Ótimo produto!&rating=5
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 13. Processar Pagamento
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments/process?orderId=1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 14. Gerar Relatório
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reports/generate?start=2023-12-01T00:00:00&end=2023-12-31T23:59:59&products=1,2,3
Content-Type: application/json

